DISJ_LEFT_TAC - tactic, eliminates disjunctive assumption causing case split

DISJ_LEFT_TAC: tactic

     [ A\/B ] C
======================
 [ A ] C     [ B ] C

It produces two subgoals in which the disjunctive assumption A\/B has been
replaced by the assumption A or B.  Disjunction elimination is also available
with STRIP_THM_TAC.
